=head1 DESCRIPTION

Provides summary information of an alert's history.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> AlertStatus => Str

The current alert status of an alert.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> CreationTime => Str

A timestamp that indicates when the first alert transition occurred in
an alert history. An alert transition can be from status C<InAlert> to
C<OK>, or from C<OK> to C<InAlert>.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> MonitoringAlertName => Str

The name of a monitoring alert.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> MonitoringScheduleName => Str

The name of a monitoring schedule.



